---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <div class="space-y-12">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Sam Boshar</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">ML Research Engineer</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I am a research engineer @ <a href="https://www.instadeep.com/">InstaDeep</a> (now <a href="https://www.biontech.com/int/en/home.html">BioNTech</a>), where I work on developing generative foundation models for genomics <i class="fa-solid fa-dna"></i>. This work builds on my masters <a href="https://dspace.mit.edu/handle/1721.1/156816?show=full">thesis</a> where I studied transformers as unified approach to model genomics and proteomics.
      </p>
      <p>
        I earned my undergraduate at MIT where I double majored in Computer Science <i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i> and Math and minored in Brain and Cognitive Sciences <i class="fa-solid fa-brain"></i>.
      </p>
      <p>
        I am most passionate about applying machine learning to solve otherwise intractable problems in science <i class="fa-solid fa-flask-vial"></i>.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
